Protein-intrinsic feature data in MAPD

Source: R/featureDat.R
featureDat.Rd

The collection and processing of the data are fully described in our manuscript.

data(featureDat)

Format

A data frame, including all human proteins (row) and their features.

Examples

data(featureDat)
